Era : Ares Planning

Space flight game.

Diffrent class ships. Upgrade ship throughtout the game. 


1 Main game mode:
Each team has a base. A base has repairs and shop. 

Base defense: turret(manned- smaller, self-controlled are stronger), flying drones?, walking drones?, sheild(s?)

Each base contains a core which is the objective to destroy. 

2 Dogfight game mode: (doing this 2nd for testing purpose)

Space port that enemies can't enter. 

Battle in that area between two bases. Ships cost money and each team only has a certain amount of money. 

3 Training grounds: (do first for testing purpose)
To test ships. 
Will be only single player. 
Target shots. 
